{"tid":2347466,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"心思思想大手入.... 大家點睇TESLA 2021走勢","createTime":"2020-12-31T05:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T09:10:25.000Z","uid":275872,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"427a21ff992ae2e68e9412767f2f142b0afa4ff3","tid":2347466,"uid":275872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T05:18:14.000Z","msg":"但又見到好多唱淡...<br />\n點好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/tesla%E6%88%96%E6%88%901999%E5%B9%B4%E7%A7%91%E7%B6%B2%E8%82%A1%E7%BF%BB%E7%89%88-103521701.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2Ftesla%25E6%2588%2596%25E6%2588%25901999%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25A7%2591%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E8%2582%25A1%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E7%2589%2588-103521701.html&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm3brkFmDP3UEX6OAVSOiSMc%3D&h=adfb495b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/tesla%E6%88%96%E6%88%901999%E5%B9%B4%E7%A7%91%E7%B6%B2%E8%82%A1%E7%BF%BB%E7%89%88-103521701.html</a><br />\n<br />\n然而，Tesla的拋物線升勢將再次造成巨大挾空倉(short squeeze)。Tesla是最被做空的上市公司，這已經是公開秘密，由於沽空賣家的損失沒有上限，他們的補倉需求可能推高升勢。<br />\n<br />\n我們早已見過此情況，Tesla股東難有完滿結局<br />\n事實上，歷史告訴我們這種走勢難以持續。我們不能預測Tesla股票短期內可升至多高，但幾乎可以肯定，投資者難有完滿結局。<br />\n<br />\n唱好Tesla，把升勢合理化的最重要論點，是Tesla不單純是一間汽車公司。好友認為買入Tesla，即代表買入汽車科技。但這種論調有致命缺陷，左右每項重大潛力股 ─ 投資者總是高估新科技的應用和影響力。<br />\n<br />\n公司經營業績亦遠不及您所想般造好。Tesla產量大增，且的確連續兩季錄得利潤。但採用公認會計原則(GAAP)，並撇除部分一次性升幅，便能看清事實：2019年全年股東應佔GAAP虧損為8.62億美元，與2018年全年9.76億美元的GAAP淨虧損相比，只有輕微改善。在沒有稅項抵免和連串一次性優惠下，Tesla經營業績的吸引力便大減。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E5%BE%9E%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E8%AA%8D%E8%AD%98%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F-%E5%BD%AD%E5%8D%9A-tesla%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%8D%E5%B0%87%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%8F%97%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85-%E8%94%9A%E4%BE%86-%E5%B0%8F%E9%B5%AC-064128613.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E5%25BE%259E%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2593%259A%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25AD%2598%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F-%25E5%25BD%25AD%25E5%258D%259A-tesla%25E5%259C%25A8%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25BD%258D%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2584%2585-%25E8%2594%259A%25E4%25BE%2586-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E9%25B5%25AC-064128613.html&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm3brkFmDP3UEX6OAVSOiSMc%3D&h=d1af1445\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E5%BE%9E%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E8%AA%8D%E8%AD%98%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F-%E5%BD%AD%E5%8D%9A-tesla%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%8D%E5%B0%87%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%8F%97%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85-%E8%94%9A%E4%BE%86-%E5%B0%8F%E9%B5%AC-064128613.html</a><br />\n<br />\n今年以來Tesla升勢凌厲，自去年在中國上海廠量產後，汽車銷量疫市攀升，今年在中國銷量更超過12萬輛。但是《彭博》引述專家指出，隨著蔚來、小鵬、理想等中國國產電動車崛起，Tesla明年在中國市場的地位將受到威脅。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Xi2dZSXDqkCmowWtIAAXpQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/R7z5NI2cCBLcSF7sG630ng--~B/aD0xMjAwO3c9MTIwMDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant/business_digest_949/ba152114315701f5a1ce25062ce89ca8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FXi2dZSXDqkCmowWtIAAXpQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FR7z5NI2cCBLcSF7sG630ng--~B%2FaD0xMjAwO3c9MTIwMDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant%2Fbusiness_digest_949%2Fba152114315701f5a1ce25062ce89ca8&h=fc0ca429&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54b4b426baed34e991a1e75e4fa3b07a59e20dbe","tid":2347466,"uid":275872,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T05:19:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E8%B3%87%E7%AE%A1%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8ceo-%E8%B3%AD-%E9%8B%AA-%E5%A5%BD%E9%81%8E%E8%B2%B7tesla-214500703.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E8%25B3%2587%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8ceo-%25E8%25B3%25AD-%25E9%258B%25AA-%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E9%2581%258E%25E8%25B2%25B7tesla-214500703.html&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm3brkFmDP3UEX6OAVSOiSMc%3D&h=7168e7cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E8%B3%87%E7%AE%A1%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8ceo-%E8%B3%AD-%E9%8B%AA-%E5%A5%BD%E9%81%8E%E8%B2%B7tesla-214500703.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>資管公司CEO：「賭一鋪」好過買Tesla</strong><br />\n<br />\n美國電動車生產商特斯拉（Tesla）雖本月加入標指成分股，但估值屢遭質疑。資產管理公司Farr, Miller ＆ Washington行政總裁Michael Farr指特斯拉估值過高，入市買其股票，不如到拉斯維加斯賭場「博一鋪」更好，因後者賭輸了，還會有一杯免費雞尾酒作「安慰獎」。<br />\n<br />\nFarr援引多項數據證明其觀點，例如股價本年至今經已升了690%，市值達6,170億美元，在標準普爾500指數公司之中排名第六貴，更為著名車廠美國福特、通用汽車，以及日本豐田3家公司加起來的兩倍。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，目前標普500公司的2021年市盈率僅22.3倍，但特斯拉卻達168倍！雖然市場估計該公司未來幾年盈利會較快增長，但至2024年市盈率仍達77倍。如以市銷率（Price to Sales ratio）計，標普500公司平均為2.7倍，特斯拉則達13倍。"},{"pid":"83edd1a4a049caadfd177f70a673e16170622173","tid":2347466,"uid":4959,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T05:21:11.000Z","msg":"Tsla年年都唱淡嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf875d24ef3877f4bdc62c2ec1001753f903f470","tid":2347466,"uid":26711,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T05:25:52.000Z","msg":"一路唱淡一路升<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73a57322ca4282101c7a8a18863dddceeaa3ed29","tid":2347466,"uid":113074,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T05:28:49.000Z","msg":"一年集資幾次<br />\n每次集資都加高鑽石底<br />\n點撚睇空"},{"pid":"9458d92f842b162c6b1742ab395990319002f2c7","tid":2347466,"uid":64060,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T05:30:48.000Z","msg":"等如支那狗一路話杯美國貨一路爆買iPhone ，身體最誠實，等緊支狗爆買Tesla"},{"pid":"6ebd02866af1739dfaa51352761c313d179b3a40","tid":2347466,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T0